headline: Consumers Energy Alerts Michiganders to Stay on Guard, Protect Themselves Against Scams
summary: Consumers Energy is reminding our Michigan friends and neighbors to be alert and take action to protect themselves from scams as we approach the holidays and with Utility Scam Awareness Day taking place this week.
